Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 4 Theories on How Orange Is the New Black Season 5 Will Start 
The next season of Orange Is the New Black is still months away, but now that we have a premiere date and a teaser, we're already excited. We have a few details about the next season (including the surprising timeline ), plus an all-too-brief teaser and a premiere date . The biggest question on our minds though, is how will season five start, given that season four ends on such an insane cliffhanger ? Here are our theories for how the new episodes will kick off.
